  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-oneblockafk\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#oneblockafk\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>OneBlockAFK</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/OneBlockAFK\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/66d7fee2aadab186cf1614c06b2258cd7078979f78cc8f3037d66aaafd9bbfa7/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e73746174652f4f6e65426c6f636b41464b\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.state/OneBlockAFK\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/OneBlockAFK\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/302835714305d6806d6bc68452af7728cc244061a1bd0ce5289c34d30525a651/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e6170692f4f6e65426c6f636b41464b\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.api/OneBlockAFK\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/OneBlockAFK\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/6ec46850afe2dba1a79f5443b9b7e8dd374ffb91d411ae4b7ef05fad887e5406/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e646c2e746f74616c2f4f6e65426c6f636b41464b\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.dl.total/OneBlockAFK\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/OneBlockAFK\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/17800cb0dc8350961b7d4e7f9d4e2e969373af78906d82a74e5c2269eb80485e/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e646c2f4f6e65426c6f636b41464b\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.dl/OneBlockAFK\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>A plugin that blocks player's being afk on block(s), if they are using Spleef use this to disallow people camping.</p>\n<p>Easy and useful!</p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-todo\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#todo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>TODO</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>maybe air and liquids</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-helpsuggestionbug-report\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#helpsuggestionbug-report\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Help/Suggestion/Bug Report</h1>\n<p>For help: <a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/OneBlockAFK/issues\">https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/OneBlockAFK/issues</a></p>\n<p>To connect me or suggest me some ideas: <a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/OguzhanUmutlu/milestone/1\">https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/OguzhanUmutlu/milestone/1</a></p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-changelog\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#changelog\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Changelog</h1>\n<p>v1.0.0 - Added main things.</p>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
